Package main.adt

Class LinkedDictionary<K extends Comparable<? super K>,V>

java.lang.Object
main.adt.LinkedDictionary<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - A comparable value to be used as a key
V - The data type to be used for the value
All Implemented Interfaces:
DictionaryInterface<K,V>
public class LinkedDictionary<K extends Comparable<? super K>,V> extends Object implements DictionaryInterface<K,V>
A class that implements the ADT dictionary by using a chain of linked nodes. The dictionary is sorted and has distinct search keys. Search keys and associated values are not null.
Version:
5.0
Author:
Frank M. Carrano, Timothy M. Henry
